    <div class="contents">
      <section class="section">
        <h3 class="sectiontitle">Summary</h3>
        <p class="body">JGA-SNP dataset is a frequency dataset that has aggregated variants detected from SNP-chip data
          in the
          <a target="_blank" href="https://humandbs.biosciencedbc.jp/en/">NBDC Human
            Database</a>/<a target="_blank" href="https://www.ddbj.nig.ac.jp/jga/index-e.html">Japanese
          Genotype-phenotype Archive (JGA)</a>. All JGA data for which an approval for creating secondary data has been
          obtained are to be
          aggregated. Note that no variants with 5 alternative alleles or less are included.
        </p>
        <ul class="unordered-list">
          <li>Version/Last updated: 06/01/2018</li>
          <li>Sample size: 183,884</li>
          <li>Number of detected variants: 1,966,919</li>
          <li>Number of variants after the exclusion: 1,249,724</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
